<title type="html"><![CDATA[1/20 (Thu.) Drunk driver who killed charged with homicide /  Top 20 Youtubers in Taiwan in 2021 (Host:Michael)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=585&amp;p=608#p608"><![CDATA[
Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF00BF">We will hold a zoom meeting only.</span><br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal">Session 1: Drunk driver who killed charged with homicide</span><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2022/01/13/2003771280">https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan ... 2003771280</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Why do the drunk drivers cause the tragedy again and again in Taiwan?<br />2.Is the penalty enough in Taiwan? What’s your standard?<br />3.Should the passengers sitting with a drunk driver be punished?<br />4.When can car makers develop a vehicle which can detect the smell of alcohol, so as to prevent the drunk drivers from starting the engine? <br />5.Would Singaporean caning penalty be an option? <br /><br />-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal">Session 2: Top 20 Youtubers in Taiwan in 2021</span><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.ajmarketing.io/post/top-20-youtubers-taiwan-2021">https://www.ajmarketing.io/post/top-20- ... aiwan-2021</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. How many youtubers do you know in the list?<br />2. List three social media platforms you use most.<br />3. Who are your favorite YouTube creators? What topics do you like about them? How often do you watch them?<br />4. Do you know anyone who makes YouTube videos? Do they have many subscribers?<br />5. People say the best thing about YouTube is anyone can do it. What are your thoughts on this statement?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25437">Michael</a> — Fri Jan 14, 2022 11:31 pm</p><hr />
